    <entry>
      <title>Hello World</title>
      <link href="/posts/3eeb.html"/>
      <url>/posts/3eeb.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="/assets/js/Meting.min.js"></script><p>Welcome to <a href="https://hexo.io/">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues">GitHub</a>.</p><h2 id="Quick-Start"><a href="#Quick-Start" class="headerlink" title="Quick Start"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id="Create-a-new-post"><a href="#Create-a-new-post" class="headerlink" title="Create a new post"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html">Writing</a></p><h3 id="Run-server"><a href="#Run-server" class="headerlink" title="Run server"></a>Run server</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html">Server</a></p><h3 id="Generate-static-files"><a href="#Generate-static-files" class="headerlink" title="Generate static files"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html">Generating</a></p><h3 id="Deploy-to-remote-sites"><a href="#Deploy-to-remote-sites" class="headerlink" title="Deploy to remote sites"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html">Deployment</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>markdown写法记录</title>
      <link href="/posts/8ffd.html"/>
      <url>/posts/8ffd.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="/assets/js/Meting.min.js"></script><h1 id="markdown写法记录"><a href="#markdown写法记录" class="headerlink" title="markdown写法记录"></a>markdown写法记录</h1><h2 id="段落语法"><a href="#段落语法" class="headerlink" title="段落语法"></a>段落语法</h2><blockquote><p>要创建段落，请使用<strong>空白行</strong>将一行或多行文本进行分隔。不要用空格或制表符缩进段落。</p></blockquote><h2 id="引用语法"><a href="#引用语法" class="headerlink" title="引用语法"></a>引用语法</h2><blockquote><p><strong>要创建块引用，请在段落前添加一个 <code>&gt;</code> 符号。</strong></p></blockquote><h2 id="换行语法"><a href="#换行语法" class="headerlink" title="换行语法"></a>换行语法</h2><blockquote><p>在文章最后添加<strong>两个空格</strong>然后回车键换行</p></blockquote><h2 id="强调语法"><a href="#强调语法" class="headerlink" title="强调语法"></a>强调语法</h2><blockquote><p><strong>要加粗文本，请在单词或短语的前后各添加两个星号或下划线</strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p><em>要用斜体显示文本，请在单词或短语前后添加一个星号或下划线</em></p></blockquote><blockquote><p><em><strong>要同时用粗体和斜体突出显示文本，请在单词或短语的前后各添加三个星号或下划线。</strong></em></p></blockquote><h2 id="代码语法"><a href="#代码语法" class="headerlink" title="代码语法"></a>代码语法</h2><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title function_">print</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;这里是代码段&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="链接语法"><a href="#链接语法" class="headerlink" title="链接语法"></a>链接语法</h2><p><a href="https://markdown.com.cn/">Markdown语法</a>。</p><h3 id="给链接增加-Title"><a href="#给链接增加-Title" class="headerlink" title="给链接增加 Title"></a>给链接增加 Title</h3><p>这是一个链接 <a href="https://markdown.com.cn/" title="最好的markdown教程">Markdown语法</a>。</p><h3 id="网址和Email地址"><a href="#网址和Email地址" class="headerlink" title="网址和Email地址"></a>网址和Email地址</h3><p><a href="https://markdown.com.cn/">https://markdown.com.cn</a><br><a href="mailto:&#102;&#x61;&#107;&#x65;&#64;&#x65;&#x78;&#97;&#x6d;&#x70;&#108;&#x65;&#46;&#99;&#111;&#109;">&#102;&#x61;&#107;&#x65;&#64;&#x65;&#x78;&#97;&#x6d;&#x70;&#108;&#x65;&#46;&#99;&#111;&#109;</a></p><h2 id="图片语法"><a href="#图片语法" class="headerlink" title="图片语法"></a>图片语法</h2><p><img src="/markdown%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/image-20240607145454960-7743305.png" alt="image-20240607145454960"></p><h3 id="链接图片"><a href="#链接图片" class="headerlink" title="链接图片"></a>链接图片</h3><blockquote><p>不知道为啥写不对 <a href="https://markdown.com.cn/"><img src="markdown写法记录/image-20240607145454960-7743305.png" alt="image-20240607145454960" style="zoom:25%;" /></a></p></blockquote><h2 id="表格写法"><a href="#表格写法" class="headerlink" title="表格写法"></a>表格写法</h2><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">| Syntax      | Description |</span><br><span class="line">| ----------- | ----------- |</span><br><span class="line">| Header      | Title       |</span><br><span class="line">| Paragraph   | Text        |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th>Syntax</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Header</td><td>Title</td></tr><tr><td>Paragraph</td><td>Text</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="删除线写法"><a href="#删除线写法" class="headerlink" title="删除线写法"></a>删除线写法</h2><p><del>我被删除了</del> 这里是删除线</p><h2 id="任务列表语法"><a href="#任务列表语法" class="headerlink" title="任务列表语法"></a>任务列表语法</h2><ul><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> Write the press release</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> Update the website</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Contact the media</li></ul><h2 id="使用-Emoji-表情"><a href="#使用-Emoji-表情" class="headerlink" title="使用 Emoji 表情"></a>使用 Emoji 表情</h2><h3 id="复制和粘贴表情符号"><a href="#复制和粘贴表情符号" class="headerlink" title="复制和粘贴表情符号"></a>复制和粘贴表情符号</h3><p><a href="https://gist.github.com/rxaviers/7360908">表情符号简码列表</a></p><h3 id="使用表情符号简码"><a href="#使用表情符号简码" class="headerlink" title="使用表情符号简码"></a>使用表情符号简码</h3><p>真好笑！ :joy: :smiley:</p><p><a href="https://gist.github.com/rxaviers/7360908">表情符号简码列表</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
